title: Five Nights At Freddy's Series With Launcher (1,2,3,4,SL,World)
description:
Five Nights At Freddy's Series

Includes

Five Nights At Freddy's 1
Five Nights At Freddy's 2
Five Nights At Freddy's 3
Five Nights At Freddy's 4
FNAF World
FNAF: Sister Location

I also borrowed an old Sierra Collection Launcher and reset it up to make a nice
little Launcher ( And only 1 Icon) for all the games.

No Need to install Just run the simple Launcher Called Five Nights At Freddy's Series.exe
Pick the game you want to play
Be Jump Scared
Enjoy.

:)

Have Fun.

          Billetwound


PS: I have used this with both the nVidia Shield Tablet and Shield TV and works perfectly.  Just add the Launcher to the Gamestream settings and you will be good to go
